review: *** ** *** **** ****** ****** ** *********** Very efficient doctor and staff. I was suffering from high fever and throat ache and have recovered and got full follow ups from clinikk . I really appreciate your help and thank you for the treatment. Would recommend anyone who is facing medical issues, the doctors are very skilled and no unnecessary treatment and tests are done. Finally found a good clinic who is focusing on proper treatment . Sincerely Thanking the team of Clinikk health hub again for the treatment.
He is very polite and listened all problems very carefully, he gave enough time for each patient before to give proper treatment.
